suppressFormulaErrors.name: suppressFormulaErrors
suppressFormulaErrors.short_desc:
Flag to determine how formula errors should be handled
       If true, then a user error will be triggered
       If false, then an exception will be thrown

formulaError.short_desc: Error message for any error that was raised/thrown by the calculation engine

cyclicFormulaCount.short_desc: Number of iterations for cyclic formulae

getInstance.short_desc: Get an instance of this class

workbook.name: workbook
workbook.short_desc:
Injected workbook for working with a PHPExcel object,
or NULL to create a standalone claculation engine

__destruct.short_desc: Unset an instance of this class

flushInstance.name: flushInstance
flushInstance.short_desc:
Flush the calculation cache for any existing instance of this class
       but only if a PHPExcel_Calculation instance exists

getDebugLog.short_desc: Get the debuglog for this claculation engine instance

__clone.short_desc: __clone implementation. Cloning should not be allowed in a Singleton!
